        "created_at": "2020-04-09T06:45:31.894Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I haven\u2019t found any documentation for APIs which exposes the different metrics collected by FoundationDB Record Layer. The only source for metrics I have discovered so far is the FDB Status json file.</p>\n<p>So, for Record Layer specifically, are there APIs which exposes the metrics? Or if not this, are there any third party tools which can help with the same?</p>",
